  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL21">
<l>paṇiviṉāl maṉama toṉṟip pavaḷavā yaraṅka ṉārkkut</l>
<l>tuṇiviṉāl vāḻa māṭṭāt tollaineñ cēnī collāy</l>
<l>aṇiyiṉār cempo ṉāya aruvarai yaṉaiya kōyil</l>
<l>maṇiyaṉār kiṭanta vāṟṟai maṉattiṉāl niṉaikka lāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O ancient heart, which is unable to live with courage</l>
<l>for the sake of [the Lord] of Raṅgam with coral lips,</l>
<l>with the mind having united [with Him] out of veneration!</l>
<l>You tell [me]! Is it possible to determine with [our] manas the way the gem-like Lord lay</l>
<l>in the precious mountain-like Temple made with beautiful, superior gold?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
